
Kite: A Data API for Hadoop

Former name: CDK - Cloudera Development Kit.

It aims at making it easier to build systems on top of the → development/Apache/Hadoop[Hadoop ecosystem].

links:
  → http://kitesdk.org/docs/current/

  → https://github.com/cloudera/cdk

  → http://www.cloudera.com/resources/recordedwebinar/cloudera-development-kit-cdk-hadoop-application-development-made-easier.html[A webinar by Eric Sammer] in which he talks about the goals of Kite (CDK).

  → https://github.com/cloudera/cdk-examples[CDK examples on github] 
